{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":10523,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":1945,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"洞号是明文，加密方式是明文，那不还是等价于ID吗","timestamp":1592793048,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":10526,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":1945,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"支持","timestamp":1592793064,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":10527,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":1945,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"还是说您觉得可能只会暴露一个洞的信息？","timestamp":1592793065,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":10528,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":1945,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"这是怎么做到的，至少得一个数据库都没了吧","timestamp":1592793082,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":10556,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":1945,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"那么怎么获得你关注的树洞呢？","timestamp":1592793332,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":1,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":1945,"reply":5,"tag":null,"text":"改进树洞加密方式的讨论？\n\n目前我理解的是每个用户的邮箱加密后成为该用户ID，同一个用户在不同洞中发帖ID是一样的（不知理解对不对）。\n\n可是事实上并不需要知道两个洞的洞主是不是同一个人，或者一个洞的Alice是不是另一个洞的Bob，只要知道在同一个洞中同一个人是同一个人就行，那可否在一个洞的发贴人信息中加入该洞的标识再加密（比如洞号、时间戳），即用ID+洞号算出一个新ID，这样即使爆破也仅能爆出一个洞的信息，不可能全局爆破。","timestamp":1592792971,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782582,"url":"","vote":{}}}